Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:01.19,0:00:06.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这不是动画 这不是动画\Nアニメじゃない　アニメじゃない
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.19,0:00:10.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是真的\N本当のことさ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.79,0:00:14.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在大家都静静睡下的夜晚\Nみんなが寝静まった夜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:14.99,0:00:17.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从窗口眺望夜空的话\N窓から空を見ていると
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:17.69,0:00:22.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以看到很厉害的东西\Nとっても　すごいものを　見たんだ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:24.59,0:00:27.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大人们都笑者说\N大人は誰も笑いながら
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:27.59,0:00:30.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我电视看太多了\Nテレビの見過ぎと言うけど
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:30.29,0:00:33.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是我绝对绝对\N僕は　絶対に絶対に
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:33.99,0:00:36.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不会说谎\N嘘なんか言ってない
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:38.79,0:00:44.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,决不会用名为常识的眼镜\N常識と言う眼鏡で
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:45.19,0:00:49.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对我们的世界\N僕たちの世界は
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:50.59,0:00:53.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,进行窥视\Nのぞけやしないのさ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:53.59,0:00:56.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,忘记了梦想的\N夢を忘れた
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:57.59,0:01:02.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,古老的地球人啊\N古い地球人よ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:03.59,0:01:06.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这不是动画 这不是动画\Nアニメじゃない　アニメじゃない
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:06.83,0:01:09.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好奇妙的感觉\N不思議な気持ち
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:09.93,0:01:15.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这不是动画 这不是动画\Nアニメじゃない　アニメじゃない
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:16.53,0:01:19.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是真的\N本当のことさ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:21.13,0:01:24.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是真的\N本当のことさ

Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:32.26,0:01:35.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第四话 热血的马士文
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.86,0:01:54.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很好,亚加玛就这样往后退吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.38,0:02:16.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要活埋了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.60,0:02:21.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你没事吧?奇马达
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.44,0:02:24.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还算没事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.62,0:02:31.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,总算把船身掩护起来了\N奇马达先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.87,0:02:35.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请再轻摇船身两三次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.64,0:02:37.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样才藏的完美阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.15,0:02:39.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,轻摇吗?办的到吗,凯撒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.81,0:02:41.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要轻摇一点吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.85,0:02:45.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我又不是摇酒的酒保...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.66,0:03:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这么快就离开
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.60,0:03:01.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要使用信用卡支付吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.33,0:03:05.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉,我没有卡,也没有现金
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.94,0:03:11.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我用这个付帐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.25,0:03:13.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早安,马士文大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.30,0:03:15.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亚加玛呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.59,0:03:18.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,昨夜在垃圾推山中徘徊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.95,0:03:21.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我去视察殖民地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.83,0:03:22.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你回去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.97,0:03:24.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.46,0:03:26.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你这打扮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.93,0:03:28.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已经妨碍了我的任务阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.31,0:03:30.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,马士文大人!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.26,0:03:44.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亚加玛可能换地点了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.92,0:03:47.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你去侦查了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.78,0:03:51.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,队员都派去侦查了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.31,0:03:53.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会遵守大人你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.12,0:03:55.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,尽可能不流一滴血
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.86,0:03:57.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而得到亚加玛的命令的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.36,0:04:00.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想请你看一个东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.87,0:04:02.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要我去看?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.48,0:04:03.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.93,0:04:05.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要花你一点时间了\N没关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.89,0:04:17.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能不流一滴血\N就能得到亚加玛的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.43,0:04:20.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是最好的\N然后在视察殖民地的情况
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.21,0:04:23.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在哈曼大人统治地球时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.81,0:04:28.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟从沙比家\N即被选出来的人们阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.01,0:04:31.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们化成我的眼去观察地球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.46,0:04:33.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们化成我的手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.64,0:04:35.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让地球成为沙比家的\N是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.64,0:04:39.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,马士文\N是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.31,0:04:50.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很期待你喔\N是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.42,0:04:58.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以历史最久的第一殖民地\N香格里拉就拜托你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.77,0:05:02.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你去那里侦查设立我们的据点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.23,0:05:06.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,遵命\N我一定不辜负你的期待,哈曼大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.00,0:05:19.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪个笨蛋开的车?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.85,0:05:22.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,连交通讯号都不会看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.55,0:05:25.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不看红绿灯的人是你们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.23,0:05:26.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.40,0:05:28.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比查,现在不是玩的时候了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.45,0:05:29.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.70,0:05:30.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起,大叔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.98,0:05:32.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你叫我大叔?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.35,0:05:35.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,无理的家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.95,0:05:38.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不,教育那些小孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.48,0:05:40.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,带给他们梦想是我们的工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.94,0:05:43.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,活泼的小孩是最好的战力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.06,0:05:44.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.49,0:05:49.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早安,还有牛奶吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.96,0:05:52.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早安,莉娜,我有帮你留下来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.88,0:05:54.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了,三天没来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.91,0:05:57.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你还要上学,真是辛苦阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.13,0:05:59.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最近怎么一下子就卖光了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.39,0:06:04.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思,因为货物都被\N掉去港口跟十町目的医院了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.41,0:06:05.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,十町目?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.86,0:06:07.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘿,莉娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.71,0:06:09.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早安\N早安,莉娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.58,0:06:11.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们又不去上学了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.68,0:06:13.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,坐完工作我们就去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.44,0:06:16.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,骗人,你们别去找我哥哥阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.61,0:06:22.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,捷度,起来阿\N知道亚加玛在哪里了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.23,0:06:23.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.90,0:06:25.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别这样...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.54,0:06:27.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在害羞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.31,0:06:29.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快穿上衣服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.11,0:06:30.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们在干什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.54,0:06:32.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叫人赶快的是你们阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.45,0:06:34.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在拖拉下去\N亚加玛会逃掉的阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.91,0:06:37.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,伊莱,别一直大喊亚加玛\N
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.25,0:06:38.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被别人听到怎么办
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.84,0:06:39.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.93,0:06:41.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你害我们被骂了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.61,0:06:42.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的!是的!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.28,0:06:45.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.08,0:06:45.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.75,0:06:48.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.01,0:06:50.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,糟了,她来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.02,0:06:51.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要去哪里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.50,0:06:52.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.55,0:06:53.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要去亚加玛对吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.69,0:06:57.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉查出亚加玛在垃圾场阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.23,0:06:58.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可以去阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.63,0:07:00.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比查,开车了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.07,0:07:01.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,OK!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.85,0:07:03.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.41,0:07:06.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会把MS当礼物拿回来给你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.57,0:07:09.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的,我得想各办法才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.27,0:07:12.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也许可以找花小姐商量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.35,0:07:20.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那家医院?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.98,0:07:23.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么脏的地方会有什么东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.48,0:07:26.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亚加玛的伤兵住进那里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.44,0:07:31.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已经答应捐款给医院\N所以利用这关系...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.26,0:07:33.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把伤兵拿来当人质吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.56,0:07:36.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是人质,是盾牌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.09,0:07:38.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可以这样,快回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.17,0:07:42.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不准采取卑鄙手段
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.98,0:07:45.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,危险!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.07,0:07:50.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,花姊姊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.54,0:08:00.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多温柔阿,挺身保护病人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.24,0:08:02.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他等于是白衣天使阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.44,0:08:06.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你有没有受伤?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.08,0:08:07.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我没事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.78,0:08:10.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有什么我帮的上忙的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.09,0:08:11.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.26,0:08:13.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是我还得照顾这患者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.40,0:08:14.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他不能走吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.87,0:08:16.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘉美尤能走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.58,0:08:19.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他只是因为战争而失去神智
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.96,0:08:23.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原来是战争的牺牲者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.82,0:08:25.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦你了,护士小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.64,0:08:26.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不是护士小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.57,0:08:27.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他是你的兄弟吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.66,0:08:29.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是男朋友阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.05,0:08:34.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想不到这地方有你这么好的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.28,0:08:35.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里的人一定...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.92,0:08:37.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起,我...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.58,0:08:40.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对人保持应有的距离
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.46,0:08:41.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你真像个天使
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.91,0:08:44.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,花小姐\N我找你好久
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.20,0:08:45.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莉娜?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.46,0:08:47.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.15,0:08:50.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天使小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.59,0:08:54.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出淤泥而不染的花阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.69,0:08:58.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这污秽的社会会把她\N逼入悲剧的角落
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.62,0:09:02.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在她的眼中的未来\N只有一片黑暗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.59,0:09:12.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.37,0:09:14.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亚加玛在哪里啊??
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.80,0:09:16.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,应该在那里啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.63,0:09:19.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看什么的,什么都没有阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.76,0:09:23.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敌人不会照着我们希望的做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.02,0:09:25.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,找出位置是艾莉的工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.22,0:09:26.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再去找吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.60,0:09:28.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.97,0:09:33.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聚集这么多人干什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.90,0:09:36.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为了不引人注目
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.03,0:09:37.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我才叫他们做这工作的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.66,0:09:39.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其实这下面有藏炸弹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.60,0:09:41.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是诱出敌人的陷阱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.87,0:09:43.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,陷阱!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.43,0:09:45.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样会危及殖民地的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.97,0:09:47.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这各作战计划太...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.24,0:09:49.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里的爆炸不会危及城市
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.44,0:09:50.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是骑士阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.93,0:09:52.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是MS
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.62,0:09:54.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,酒瓶山?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.03,0:09:58.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为了不惊动到一般人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.65,0:10:00.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我才用这方式偷运过来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.22,0:10:02.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么用酒瓶?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.76,0:10:05.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你就不会用玫瑰花覆盖吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.92,0:10:08.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那男人是谁?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.83,0:10:10.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.70,0:10:16.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亚加玛移到前面的第二区了\N太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.05,0:10:19.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,戈图,你跟侦查部队会合,等待连络
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.05,0:10:20.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要用嘉力斯去找亚加玛\N是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.34,0:10:28.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他也想夺取亚加玛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.56,0:10:30.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被他抢先就不好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.70,0:10:32.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉,你去通知比查他们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.58,0:10:34.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那捷度你呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.30,0:10:35.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妨碍他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.43,0:10:36.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快点去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.08,0:10:48.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是MS?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.77,0:11:02.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是昨晚的家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.48,0:11:17.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,成功了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.46,0:11:26.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他真的有办法抢到Z高达吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.57,0:11:27.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.44,0:11:28.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比查
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.68,0:11:31.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在发什么呆,快点帮忙阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.87,0:11:34.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是哥哥他们的车
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.25,0:11:39.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跑到这么脏的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.36,0:11:44.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你没事吧,莉娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.77,0:11:46.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.23,0:11:51.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起,洗达,冠武\N你们先下车吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.60,0:11:54.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.54,0:11:58.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,车子要走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.05,0:12:16.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,终于装好舱口了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.19,0:12:21.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,安多拉的工程技术不错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.45,0:12:25.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,疑?关不起来吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.84,0:12:30.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用手动控制吧...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.39,0:12:38.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么声音?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.21,0:12:45.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这镜头是左后方21号镜头
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.36,0:12:50.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么?\N在正后方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.19,0:12:53.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是小偷吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.80,0:12:54.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但好面熟阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.85,0:13:08.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,后面的少年马上下去\N会受伤的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.25,0:13:10.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,难得来到这里,我不会下去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.65,0:13:13.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你是很没品...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.84,0:13:17.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别恶作剧了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.53,0:13:20.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谁会开这种危险的玩笑!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.84,0:13:21.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想干什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.37,0:13:23.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要偷MS阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.38,0:13:26.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我要先阻止你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.13,0:13:27.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你疯了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.28,0:13:28.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.45,0:13:29.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,头壳坏掉的坏小孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.06,0:13:32.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,受了伤我也不管你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.57,0:13:37.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你有准备好吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.90,0:13:38.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.99,0:13:41.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉,快把沙装入瓶子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.18,0:13:43.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,废话,我正在做阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.46,0:13:52.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ㄟ~捷度好努力阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.24,0:13:54.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,开到左边去,左边右边都行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.52,0:13:55.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,OK!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.73,0:13:58.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下去!下去!快下去!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.72,0:14:07.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,捷度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.25,0:14:08.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.13,0:14:10.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,发射了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.87,0:14:13.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.86,0:14:19.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惜,还差一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.69,0:14:21.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别停阿,快继续阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.36,0:14:24.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这些卑劣的坏小孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.26,0:14:26.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小鬼,你看不起大人吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.75,0:14:29.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谁看不起谁了啊\N我可是拼了命的阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.35,0:14:30.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.29,0:14:31.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下去吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.17,0:14:32.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.91,0:14:34.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的眼睛还...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.39,0:14:35.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可不管阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.44,0:14:36.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卑鄙!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.35,0:14:40.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,成功了,进入驾驶舱了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.80,0:14:46.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算是小孩也不可原谅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.59,0:14:51.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要把你从这里丢下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.07,0:14:58.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么?这家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.07,0:14:59.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下去!下去!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.81,0:15:01.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,捷度!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.26,0:15:03.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看脚!下去下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.58,0:15:04.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我才不下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.73,0:15:08.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再靠近,捷度,这里阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.16,0:15:10.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快点把他踢下来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.33,0:15:12.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妄想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.03,0:15:15.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,捷度!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.75,0:15:29.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小孩做这种事是不可以原谅的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.70,0:15:31.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要修理你!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.07,0:15:32.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,马士文...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.18,0:15:36.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听说就殖民社会腐败到了极点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.97,0:15:40.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个社会得小孩\N若有扭曲的行为
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.28,0:15:42.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也是因为他们是被害者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.21,0:15:47.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你应该疼爱他们,保护他们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.72,0:15:50.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哈曼大人说的对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.55,0:15:54.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为了纠正他们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.12,0:15:56.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要打倒亚加玛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.91,0:15:59.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后统治殖民地\N净化这个肮脏的社会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.76,0:16:10.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,关掉手电筒,会被发现的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.42,0:16:18.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像会塌下来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.95,0:16:20.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你别再说了,愈说就会掉越多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.85,0:16:34.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,应该不会来了吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.69,0:16:37.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不,再等等吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.18,0:16:38.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.44,0:16:42.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第二紧急舱口被打开了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.00,0:16:42.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敌人吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.92,0:16:44.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不,好像是小孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.95,0:16:45.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.80,0:16:48.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,关掉11,12通道\N把他们引诱到这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.56,0:16:49.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.93,0:16:52.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然来了,而且是由下方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.17,0:16:59.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是MS仓库吗\N
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.42,0:17:00.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像没人阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.11,0:17:02.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,糟了,是陷阱阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.41,0:17:05.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.08,0:17:07.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Z高达呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.74,0:17:10.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那里,在上面的甲板
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.13,0:17:17.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,住手阿!\N不要阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.48,0:17:20.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他接近Z高达了\N抓住他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.85,0:17:24.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又是你,这个孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.82,0:17:31.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,坐上他,就是我的东西了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.17,0:17:42.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,成功了,干的好,捷度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.95,0:17:47.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.98,0:17:53.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.37,0:17:55.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,刚才的人来了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.57,0:17:57.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.44,0:17:59.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,发现敌人,一架MS
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.51,0:18:01.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叫密达斯准备
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.18,0:18:02.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,花呢?还没到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.87,0:18:04.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把小孩带到舰桥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.81,0:18:06.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易把Z高达偷出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.60,0:18:09.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不能就这样被打坏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.16,0:18:11.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Z高达,去吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.77,0:18:19.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,舱门关起来,变成荧幕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.73,0:18:22.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,厉害,是360度荧幕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.94,0:18:26.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你若以为这样就能打倒我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.09,0:18:27.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你太差劲了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.72,0:18:35.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想逃?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.02,0:18:37.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易偷到,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.36,0:18:38.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可以让他受损
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.55,0:18:39.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.60,0:18:42.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,逃跑太卑鄙了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.18,0:18:44.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你该堂堂正正来决斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.20,0:18:48.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不想保护自己的船吗!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.81,0:18:52.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.86,0:18:56.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,使用来福枪会伤害到一般民众\N可是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.15,0:19:01.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,烦死了,又来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.98,0:19:06.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迫不得已,戈图,用陷阱吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.26,0:19:08.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要使用吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.23,0:19:11.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我现在引诱他过去,你准备陷阱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.41,0:19:12.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.72,0:19:14.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然违反骑士精神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.75,0:19:17.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是为了纠正社会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.03,0:19:18.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,觉悟吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.47,0:19:24.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是现在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.29,0:19:32.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是陷阱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.24,0:19:33.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上当了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.07,0:19:39.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.92,0:19:44.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,马士文大人,舱门没关
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.53,0:19:45.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么,关起来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.15,0:19:56.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要在宇宙对打吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.78,0:19:58.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听见吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.33,0:20:01.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,按下自动平衡按钮,在右边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.69,0:20:03.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的用你的操纵杆来操纵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.99,0:20:05.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,办的到吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.87,0:20:12.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被躲过了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.28,0:20:14.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要用这个状态打吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.33,0:20:17.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,冷静下来,你办的到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.05,0:20:20.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么?红色灯亮了,空气...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.30,0:20:22.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,空气外泄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.69,0:20:24.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,马上回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.15,0:20:25.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不能让Z高达受损
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.99,0:20:27.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,密达斯呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.08,0:20:29.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快出动了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.08,0:20:31.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是经由港口出去很花时间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.01,0:20:32.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就从同一个破洞出去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.05,0:20:42.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不会一直挨打的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.44,0:20:43.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上次是你运气好!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.93,0:20:45.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你以为你能打赢我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.16,0:20:51.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这下子我要改变未来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.62,0:20:54.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行,氧气不够了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.98,0:20:56.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂!加油
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.23,0:20:57.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,杰度!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.25,0:20:58.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,起来阿,捷度!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:05.37,0:21:06.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可恶,还有死前挣扎吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.25,0:21:09.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不会死的!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:17.14,0:21:19.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,赢了!打赢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:19.38,0:21:20.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他打赢了,舰长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.83,0:21:23.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的\N好,我们现在去找你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.68,0:21:25.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你留在原地吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.34,0:21:27.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又要拿回Z刚达了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:27.67,0:21:29.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌,我又做白工了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:29.03,0:21:30.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会请你吃ㄧ顿早餐的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:30.60,0:21:33.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后乖乖回去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:34.77,0:21:36.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想因为氧气不足而死吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:36.40,0:21:38.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道了,快点吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:38.70,0:21:40.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,马士文大人,你没事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:40.87,0:21:43.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我现在就走陷阱的洞回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:43.63,0:21:46.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是洞开始合起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:46.29,0:21:48.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么?那快阻止阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:48.69,0:21:50.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的,你这个笨蛋东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:50.60,0:21:53.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你就是这样,我才会被打败的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:56.46,0:21:58.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了,快点吧,莉娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:58.59,0:21:59.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:06.21,0:22:07.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:11.60,0:22:13.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个天使..
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:16.07,0:22:17.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要停下来吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:17.88,0:22:20.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不,没关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:20.90,0:22:23.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,邪念会带来失败
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:24.90,0:22:30.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哈曼大人\N我一定创造出你要的未来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:47.63,0:23:50.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,盖蒙这个人 在收破烂的同行里评价很不好

Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:45.10,0:22:50.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在没有道路的荒野里\N道もない荒れた原野に
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:52.10,0:22:58.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,建造铁路真是一件辛苦差事\Nレールを作るのは苦しいことさ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:00.10,0:23:01.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是\Nだけど
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:02.50,0:23:07.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可以不知晓远方\N遠い向こうも知らなくちゃいけない
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:08.70,0:23:15.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为我们的路现在才开始\N僕達は これからなんだ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:15.80,0:23:24.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人们都说我们是“忘记了梦想的小孩子”\N“夢を忘れた子供達”と 人は言う
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:25.50,0:23:32.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊啊 时代正在哭泣\Nああー 時代が泣いている

Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:50.95,0:23:53.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他成为了马士文的同伴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:53.03,0:23:56.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,花也因为卡缪没有精神而没有精神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:56.17,0:23:58.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,结果 只好让我出击了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:58.98,0:24:01.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是 Z的状态又不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:01.63,0:24:04.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这还真是烦死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:04.08,0:24:06.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下集 高达ZZ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:06.45,0:24:08.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,捷度的决心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:08.82,0:24:10.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哈哈 好像很厉害呢
